how narnia started a strange professercame upon three magic rings and tricked two children to going to a forest with lots of different pools in it when they touched the green ring they go into one of the pools and come upon a dark and dead world they come upon the white witch and they take her back to there world using the golden magic ring while back on earth they made her angry so she used her strength to break off a piece of a lightpost outside and at the last minute the two children took her to the forest and they went into the nearest pool they were taken to a world of blackness then they heard singing and they turned around to see a great lion opening his mouth and the music was coming from him then the world sprung to life and everything was growing hills formed trees grew and started walking around animals came to the world aslan the lion alled some together he said they were special and were to be protectors of the new land narnia the white witch became even more angry so she threw the lightpost at aslan but it fell short it stuck up straight in the ground and grew into a lantern this lantern symbolizes the boundary between narnia and the white witches territory then the white witch ran away into naria and the lion said that the boy and the girl must go and get the white witch to leave narnia so they went to her palace they climbed over her fence and when they couldn't persuade the white witch to leave they left taking with them a fruit from one of her trees outside then the boy took it to aslan and he said that it held the secret to eternal life and not to eat ir the boy said that his mother was gravely sick and aslan said if he wished to give it to her then she would live while all her loved ones left her never dying the boy gave her a piece to save her when they went back home and then planted the seed it grew into a beautiful tree the boy grew older and watched the tree prosper then he cut down the tree when it was big enough and made a wardrobe out of 